Server init.
Program use: ['en/mailtools.xo'].

>> e-mail := HTML-Email new.
>> cid := e-mail attach: ( File new: ['poweredbyxo.png'] ).

e-mail
	from: ['xo@xoscript.com'] name: ['xo'],
	to: ( List new ; ['xo2@xoscipt.com'] ),
	subject: ['xoxo'],
	body: (['
<html>
<body>
<h1>hello!</h1>
<img src="<cid>">
</body>
</html>	
'] <cid>: cid), send.

